snippet.title: Frostpoint VR: Proving Grounds — Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Frostpoint VR: Proving Grounds is a team-based multiplayer shooter that pits two sides against each other in high-intensity PvP game modes, with a unique PvE twist. Learn more at https://www.inxile-entertainment.com/frostpointvr
